author: Riley Morgan For Daily Mail Australia
title: TigerAir offering Sydney to Brisbane flights for $19 | Daily Mail Online
text: The best sale ever? TigerAir offer flights from Sydney to Brisbane for as low as $19 in flash sale - but you'll have to be quick TigerAir flash sale deals from Sydney to Brisbane one way for $19 Sydneysiders can fly to Cairns one way for as low as $39 TigerAir's insane flash sale ends on February 25 at 4pm Published: 02:26 GMT, 25 February 2017 | Updated: 02:58 GMT, 25 February 2017 102 shares comments Tiger Air have launched a tantalising flash sale with flights from as low as $19. Travellers looking to escape the hustle and bustle of Sydney can fly to Brisbane for just $19 one way in their Saturday flight fever. TigerAir are also offering the reverse flight from Brisbane to Sydney for $19. TigerAir's insane flash sale ends at 4pm on February 25 Sydneysiders looking to go further north can fly to Cairns for just $39, but both wild fares are only on sale today ending at 4pm on February 25. If the Gold Coast is your destination of choice travellers from Sydney can jet off for only $59 one way. RELATED ARTICLES
